Package: bubblegam
Title: Geodata preprocessing, plotting & bubble animation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
    person("Georg", "Starz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "georgstarz99@gmail.com"),
    person("Anna", "Bischof", role = "aut", email = "anna.julia.bischof@gmail.com"))
Description: A package to efficiently merge (geo)dataframes, 
    identify, and move spatial outliers in geodata, and create 
    geographic plots, bubbleplots and the animation between these plots.
URL: https://github.com/Geo-99/bubblegam
BugReports: https://github.com/Geo-99/bubblegam/issues
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    animation,
    dplyr,
    sf,
    lwgeom,
    magick,
    transformr
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
